Will:
<i> Jack.</i>

33:10.489 --> 33:11.788
Jack?

33:14.226 --> 33:15.492
What?

33:20.632 --> 33:22.332
Oh for chrissake, Will.

33:28.674 --> 33:30.374
Jack:
<i> Ah, the water's freezing.</i>

33:37.716 --> 33:39.616
Will:
<i> Thanks for taking care of me.</i>

33:40.285 --> 33:41.551
<i> You're</i>

33:43.322 --> 33:44.588
<i> like a dad.</i>

33:45.190 --> 33:46.456
Jesus, Will.

33:47.659 --> 33:49.359
I'm not our goddamn father.

33:51.063 --> 33:53.030
You're what I
imagine he would be.

33:54.166 --> 33:55.632
Don't say that.

33:57.836 --> 33:59.302
He was a soldier.

34:00.072 --> 34:01.638
He got shot.

34:02.608 --> 34:04.074
Will:
<i> But that made him a hero.</i>

34:06.979 --> 34:08.211
It didn't.

34:12.918 --> 34:14.184
Will:
<i> Jack?</i>

34:15.754 --> 34:17.454
<i> Why wasn't he a hero?</i>

34:20.592 --> 34:22.659
He was shot by his
commanding officer.

34:24.630 --> 34:25.929
What?

34:27.399 --> 34:28.665
Why?

34:30.969 --> 34:32.469
Why do you think?

34:45.851 --> 34:47.150
Vernon:
<i> Wake up.</i>

