39:56.261 --> 39:57.961
<i> that was very brave.</i>

39:59.931 --> 40:01.197
Take this.

40:02.167 --> 40:03.466
<i> Go on.</i>

40:03.468 --> 40:04.768
<i> Take it.</i>

40:04.770 --> 40:06.870
<i> When this is all over,</i>

40:06.872 --> 40:08.204
it's yours to keep.

40:08.206 --> 40:09.506
Thank you.

40:13.044 --> 40:15.178
Robert, get on the boat.

40:15.180 --> 40:16.679
