48:01.813 --> 48:03.079
Arthur:
<i> Mark?</i>

48:10.555 --> 48:11.787
No.

48:22.467 --> 48:23.833
Vernon:
<i> Hey wait, wait.</i>

48:23.835 --> 48:25.167
