if it dries.

48:29.540 --> 48:30.673
I-I don't want it.

48:30.675 --> 48:31.807
I'll take it off.

48:31.809 --> 48:33.009
He doesn't want it.

48:33.011 --> 48:34.911
It's for his parents.

48:54.565 --> 48:56.732
<i> Ray, take his place.</i>

49:02.740 --> 49:04.140
Teach us, O Lord,

49:04.142 --> 49:05.274
true brotherhood,

49:05.276 --> 49:07.777
in daily thought and deed.

49:07.779 --> 49:10.012
(in unison) That we may
tread with humble heart,

49:10.014 --> 49:12.381
the path where
Thou dost lead.

49:12.383 --> 49:15.051
Love then shall reign
supreme over all,

49:15.053 --> 49:17.753
over heart and
mind and hand.

49:17.755 --> 49:20.056
Eternal love and brotherhood.

49:20.058 --> 49:21.791
In all this storm tossed-

49:21.793 --> 49:22.892
Fuck!

