49:23.895 --> 49:25.411
Arthur:
<i> Waller.</i>

49:25.412 --> 49:26.928
Thanks, Ray, but praying's
not going to help Mark.

49:26.931 --> 49:28.130
<i> It's not gonna save us.</i>

49:28.132 --> 49:29.131
<i> We can't right the canoe.</i>

49:29.133 --> 49:30.299
<i> We got no paddles.</i>

49:30.301 --> 49:31.934
