<i> You know what?</i>
<i> Go, Ray.</i>

49:43.147 --> 49:44.146
<i> It's better than praying.</i>

49:44.148 --> 49:45.581
Why not do something useful?

49:45.583 --> 49:47.917
No one's going anywhere
by themselves.

49:47.919 --> 49:49.418
<i> As a team maybe.</i>

49:49.420 --> 49:50.920
<i> But not you, Ray.</i>

49:50.922 --> 49:52.355
I see a light.

49:53.024 --> 49:54.190
Momma?

49:54.192 --> 49:55.491
Wait.
-<i> Momma?</i>

49:55.960 --> 49:56.959
Ray!
-Momma.

49:56.961 --> 49:58.761
Momma, Momma?
-Ray!

49:58.763 --> 50:00.429
Momma, Momma?
Arthur:<i> Ray.</i>

50:00.431 --> 50:01.897
