50:07.739 --> 50:09.038
Ray!
-Momma.

50:09.507 --> 50:10.840
Momma.

50:10.842 --> 50:12.408
<i> Momma.</i>

50:12.410 --> 50:13.909
Arthur:
<i> Ray, come back here!</i>

50:15.213 --> 50:16.712
<i> Ray, come back here.</i>

50:17.248 --> 50:21.017
(gentle instrumental)

50:21.019 --> 50:22.284
Ray:
<i> Momma?</i>

50:22.687 --> 50:23.953
<i> Momma.</i>

