51:43.968 --> 51:45.468
What? No, no, no way.

51:45.470 --> 51:47.002
I'll go alone if I have to.

51:47.004 --> 51:48.370
Fine.

51:48.372 --> 51:50.840
Oliver:
<i> Mr. Butcher left</i>
<i> you in charge.</i>

51:50.842 --> 51:51.841
I'll go with Vernon, we-

51:51.843 --> 51:52.908
No, go by yourself!

51:52.910 --> 51:54.577
Because swimming out
there is suicide.

51:54.579 --> 51:55.778
You're a pussy.

51:55.780 --> 51:57.346
I can't swim straight in this.

51:57.348 --> 51:59.014
I can't follow a goddamn star!

51:59.016 --> 52:00.216
Or I'll push you off.

52:00.218 --> 52:01.550
Waller!

52:03.421 --> 52:04.687
Whoa.

