52:18.236 --> 52:20.302
That makes you my
second in command.

52:20.304 --> 52:23.639
Your attitude can
save us or sink us.

52:23.641 --> 52:25.141
So what's it gonna be?

52:25.676 --> 52:28.277
(muffled screaming)

52:28.279 --> 52:31.013
Do you hear how
scared they are?

52:32.483 --> 52:35.317
(muffled screaming)

