the accident.

53:29.207 --> 53:30.472
Jack:
<i> Don't say that.</i>

53:34.612 --> 53:36.445
It was Butcher's fault.

53:36.447 --> 53:37.446
What, Vern?

53:37.448 --> 53:38.614
I said it was
Mr. Butcher's fault.

53:38.616 --> 53:40.216
Waller:
<i> You dope, what do you know?</i>

53:40.218 --> 53:41.684
